[
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "(8:23)<n id=\"1\" /> The <st data-num=\"04155\" class=\"\">gloom</st> will be <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">dispelled</st> for <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">those who</st> were <st data-num=\"04164\" class=\"\">anxious</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">In <st data-num=\"07223\" class=\"\">earlier</st> <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">times</st> he<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">humiliated</st><p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"02074\" class=\"\">Zebulun</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"05321\" class=\"\">Naphtali</st>;<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">but <st data-num=\"0314\" class=\"\">now</st> he <st data-num=\"03513\">brings honor</st><n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">to the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">way</st> of the <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">sea</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"05676\" class=\"\">region beyond</st> the <st data-num=\"03383\" class=\"\">Jordan</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"01551\" class=\"\">Galilee</st> of the <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st>.<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">(9:1) The <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">walking</st> in <st data-num=\"02822\">darkness</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> a <st data-num=\"01419\" class=\"\">bright</st> <st data-num=\"0216\" class=\"\">light</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0216\" class=\"\">light</st> <st data-num=\"05050\" class=\"\">shines</st> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> those who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in a <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> of <st data-num=\"06757\" class=\"\">deep darkness</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">You<n id=\"1\" /> have <st data-num=\"07235\" class=\"\">enlarged</st> the <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nation</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">you <st data-num=\"01431\" class=\"\">give</st> them <st data-num=\"01431\" class=\"\">great</st> <st data-num=\"08057\" class=\"\">joy</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"08055\" class=\"\">rejoice</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">in</st> your <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">presence</st><p class=\"poetry\">as <st data-num=\"07105\" class=\"\">harvesters</st> <st data-num=\"08057\" class=\"\">rejoice</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">as</st> warriors <st data-num=\"01523\" class=\"\">celebrate</st><n id=\"3\" /> when they <st data-num=\"02505\" class=\"\">divide up</st> the <st data-num=\"07998\" class=\"\">plunder</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> their <st data-num=\"05448\" class=\"\">oppressive</st> <st data-num=\"05923\" class=\"\">yoke</st><p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"04294\" class=\"\">club</st> that strikes their <st data-num=\"07926\" class=\"\">shoulders</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"07626\" class=\"\">cudgel</st> the <st data-num=\"05065\" class=\"\">oppressor</st> uses on them,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">you have <st data-num=\"02865\" class=\"\">shattered</st>, as in the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> of <st data-num=\"04080\" class=\"\">Midian\u2019s</st> defeat.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Indeed</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"05430\" class=\"\">boot</st> that <st data-num=\"05431\" class=\"\">marches</st> and <st data-num=\"07494\" class=\"\">shakes the earth</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and every <st data-num=\"08071\" class=\"\">garment</st> <st data-num=\"01556\" class=\"\">dragged</st> through <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">blood</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">is</st> <st data-num=\"08316\" class=\"\">used</st> as <st data-num=\"03980\" class=\"\">fuel</st> for the <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> a <st data-num=\"03206\" class=\"\">child</st> has been<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">born</st> to us,<p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> has been <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">given</st> to us.<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"01961 05921 07926\">shoulders</st> <st data-num=\"04951\" class=\"\">responsibility</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and is <st data-num=\"07121 08034\">called</st><n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06382\">Wonderful</st> <st data-num=\"03289\">Adviser</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"01368\" class=\"\">Mighty</st> <st data-num=\"0410\" class=\"\">God</st>,<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05703\" class=\"\">Everlasting</st> <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">Father</st>,<n id=\"6\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">Prince</st> of <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">Peace</st>.<n id=\"7\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">His <st data-num=\"04951\" class=\"\">dominion</st> will be <st data-num=\"07227\" class=\"\">vast</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and he will bring <st data-num=\"0369 07093\">immeasurable</st> <st data-num=\"07965\" class=\"\">prosperity</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He will rule <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"03678\" class=\"\">throne</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> David\u2019s <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdom</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">establishing</st> it<n id=\"4\" /> and <st data-num=\"05582\" class=\"\">strengthening</st> it<p class=\"poetry\">by promoting <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">justice</st> and <st data-num=\"06666\" class=\"\">fairness</st>,<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">from <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">this time</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">forward</st> and <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">forevermore</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"07068\" class=\"\">zeal</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st><n id=\"6\" /> will <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">accomplish</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><n id=\"1\" /> The <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">decreed</st> <st data-num=\"01697\">judgment</st><n id=\"3\" /> on <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and it <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fell</st> on <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">were aware</st><n id=\"1\" /> of it,<p class=\"poetry\">the people of <st data-num=\"0669\" class=\"\">Ephraim</st> and those <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">living</st> in <st data-num=\"08111\" class=\"\">Samaria</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Yet with <st data-num=\"01346\" class=\"\">pride</st> and an <st data-num=\"01433\" class=\"\">arrogant</st> <st data-num=\"03824\" class=\"\">attitude</st>, they <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cThe <st data-num=\"03843\" class=\"\">bricks</st> have <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fallen</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">but we will <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">rebuild</st> with <st data-num=\"01496\" class=\"\">chiseled stone</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"08256\" class=\"\">sycamore fig trees</st> have been <st data-num=\"01438\" class=\"\">cut down</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">but we will <st data-num=\"02498\" class=\"\">replace</st> them with <st data-num=\"0730\" class=\"\">cedars</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Then the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"07682\" class=\"\">provoked</st><n id=\"1\" /> their <st data-num=\"06862\" class=\"\">adversaries</st> to <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">attack</st> them,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"05526\" class=\"\">stirred up</st><n id=\"3\" /> their <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st>\u2014</p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0758\" class=\"\">Syria</st> from the <st data-num=\"06924\" class=\"\">east</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"06430\" class=\"\">Philistines</st> from the <st data-num=\"0268\" class=\"\">west</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"0398 03605 06310\">gobbled up</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israelite</st> territory.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Despite <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>, his <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st> does <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">subside</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and his <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> is <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">ready to strike</st> <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">again</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">return</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> the one who <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">struck</st> them,<p class=\"poetry\">they did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01875\" class=\"\">seek reconciliation</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">So the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03772\" class=\"\">cut off</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st> and <st data-num=\"02180\" class=\"\">tail</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">both the <st data-num=\"03712\" class=\"\">shoots</st> and <st data-num=\"0100\" class=\"\">stalk</st><n id=\"1\" /> in <st data-num=\"0259\" class=\"\">one</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"02205\" class=\"\">leaders</st> and the <st data-num=\"05375 06440\">highly respected people</st><n id=\"1\" /> are the <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophets</st> who <st data-num=\"03384\" class=\"\">teach</st> <st data-num=\"08267\" class=\"\">lies</st> are the <st data-num=\"02180\" class=\"\">tail</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"0833\" class=\"\">leaders</st> of <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">nation</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">were</st> <st data-num=\"08582\" class=\"\">misleading</st> people,<p class=\"poetry\">and the people being <st data-num=\"0833\" class=\"\">led</st> were <st data-num=\"01104\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921 03651\">So</st> the <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Lord</st> was <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08055\" class=\"\">pleased</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\">with</st> their <st data-num=\"0970\" class=\"\">young men</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"07355\" class=\"\">took</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"07355\" class=\"\">pity</st><n id=\"2\" /> on their <st data-num=\"03490\" class=\"\">orphans</st> and <st data-num=\"0490\" class=\"\">widows</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\">for</st> the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> nation was <st data-num=\"02611\" class=\"\">godless</st><n id=\"3\" /> and <st data-num=\"07489\" class=\"\">did wicked things</st>,<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">mouth</st> was <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">speaking</st> <st data-num=\"05039\" class=\"\">disgraceful words</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Despite <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>, his <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st> does <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">subside</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and his <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> is <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">ready to strike</st> <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">again</st>.<n id=\"6\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07564\" class=\"\">evil</st> <st data-num=\"01197\" class=\"\">burned</st> like a <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">it <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">consumed</st> <st data-num=\"08068\" class=\"\">thorns</st> and <st data-num=\"07898\" class=\"\">briers</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">it <st data-num=\"03341\" class=\"\">burned up</st> the <st data-num=\"05442\" class=\"\">thickets</st> of the <st data-num=\"03293\" class=\"\">forest</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and they <st data-num=\"055\" class=\"\">went up</st> in <st data-num=\"01348 06227\">smoke</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Because of the <st data-num=\"05678\" class=\"\">anger</st> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>, the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st> was <st data-num=\"06272\" class=\"\">scorched</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">became</st> <st data-num=\"03980\" class=\"\">fuel</st> for the <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">People <st data-num=\"02550\" class=\"\">had</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"02550\" class=\"\">compassion</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st> <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">another</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"01504\" class=\"\">devoured</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"03225\" class=\"\">right</st>, but <st data-num=\"07456\" class=\"\">were</st> still <st data-num=\"07456\" class=\"\">hungry</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">ate</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"08040\" class=\"\">left</st>, but <st data-num=\"07646\" class=\"\">were</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07646\" class=\"\">satisfied</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">People</st> even <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">ate</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <st data-num=\"01320\" class=\"\">flesh</st> of their own <st data-num=\"02220\" class=\"\">arm</st>!<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "9",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04519\" class=\"\">Manasseh</st> fought against<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0669\" class=\"\">Ephraim</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0669\" class=\"\">Ephraim</st> against <st data-num=\"04519\" class=\"\">Manasseh</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">together</st> <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">they</st> fought <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>. <p class=\"poetry\">Despite <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this</st>, his <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st> does <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">subside</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and his <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> is <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">ready to strike</st> <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">again</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  }
]